      "layout": "The page exhibits a full-bleed background often featuring dynamic video or photography, over which a contained, right-aligned UI panel floats. The hero section is characterized by this overlaid panel structure. Content within the UI panel is arranged in a consistent vertical flow, featuring a main informational card followed by a scrollable list of compact product item cards. There is no strict grid for main content outside the panel, but product items within the list appear as uniform, vertically stacked elements. Navigation is minimal, consisting of a top-bar with text links and subtle indicators, while the main UI panel acts as a dynamic content display.",
